Assembly Types

Terminal Wire Assemblies

Browse our terminal wire assembly catalog by component type. All assemblies are 100% tested and available with JST, Molex, or TE compatible terminals.

Pre-Crimped Leads

Single or dual-end pre-crimped wires ready for your assembly process. Custom lengths and terminations.

Custom wire length AWG 32-14 Various terminals UL-certified

Wire-to-Board Assemblies

Board connectors with crimped wires. PH/XH/EH series for PCB connection applications.

2-15 positions 0.8-2.5mm pitch Vertical/right-angle 100% tested

Wire-to-Wire Assemblies

Male-to-female cable assemblies. Plug-and-play solutions for modular connections.

Ready-to-use Custom breaks Shielded options Color-coded

Ribbon Cable Assemblies

High-density IDC ribbon cables for compact electronics and data transmission.

High density IDC termination Pitch 1.27-2.54mm Custom length
